<refsect1 id="description-gtksheetrange">
  <title>Description</title>

  <para>
  <link linkend="class-gtksheetrange">
  <classname>gtkseet.SheetRange</classname></link> is an object holding data about a range of cells. It is used
  to specify a range of cells when calling several <link linkend="class-gtksheet">
  <classname>gtksheet.Sheet</classname></link> methods.
  </para>
  <para>
  The range of cells specified by a <classname>gtkseet.SheetRange</classname> 
  starts with the top-left cell indicated by "row0" and "col0" attributes to the
  bottom-right cell indicated by "rowi" and "coli".
  </para>

</refsect1>

